{"tid":1097402,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"睇完馬會賠率，我有強烈預感曼聯會輸","createTime":"2019-04-08T11:02:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-10T21:38:38.000Z","uid":43785,"like":45,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"89e618aeef6acbaa8ed24eb29f25a0bc95acf1ae","tid":1097402,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T11:02:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TJp0o8t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTJp0o8t.jpg&h=7df46f66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好撚老實，今年曼聯係英超風光不再， 只係第六位。 蘇斯克查根本心裏面清楚知道，後防冇一個人可以應付美斯。<br />\n而巴塞係西甲第一位。 加上巴塞有球王美斯坐鎮。 美斯今年狀態大好，入球同助攻再創新高。<br />\n<br />\n此消彼長之下， 兩對根本冇得踢。<br />\n<br />\n即使係作客，巴塞輸嘅機率都係係零。<br />\n<br />\n暫時睇八強入面呢8隊波，係呢一刻，沒有一隊能夠戰勝今年嘅巴塞隆拿。"},{"pid":"4b752805e68752935b72f9dfa0083f35af5dfa01","tid":1097402,"uid":166743,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T11:03:55.000Z","msg":"環保<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57e6a6bb28673f34156cbef29391b42a46c1e08d","tid":1097402,"uid":43785,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T11:04:23.000Z","msg":"真金不怕洪爐火， <br />\n正確分析巴塞隆拿對曼聯賽果。"},{"pid":"0df9569f184f5aa61e66b435d87da4f5d284073b","tid":1097402,"uid":43785,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T11:33:07.000Z","msg":"我朋友啱啱同我講<br />\n作為曼聯球迷， 呢場波都唔知睇唔睇好<br />\n望住一100%會輸嘅波<br />\n好心UP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c007097f500378e58a8ead550aaedacebfc7b2c","tid":1097402,"uid":75610,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T11:34:42.000Z","msg":"有乜可能淨係受讓平半<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申獌狗"},{"pid":"f8fa941fb463c99ff4d0f1fd1dd0f3deeb5aaf41","tid":1097402,"uid":138177,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T11:46:49.000Z","msg":"比d咁ga對手魚拉突..<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b75fcd07